==Romanian==
===Etymology===
It is agreed to be from PIE ''*del-'', "to split, carve, cut", but whether it is a substratum word, akin to Albanian ''[[daltë]]'', or an early loan from Common Slavic *''dolto'' (compare e.g. Slovak ''[[dlato]]'') is disputed.
===Noun===
'''daltă''' {{f}}, pl. ''dălţi''

